Purpose: 

    This program allows the user to sign in and sign out books at a library.

header files (if any):

    #include <stdio.h>
    #include <stdlib.h>
    #include <string.h>
    #include <unistd.h>
    #include <signal.h>
    #include <sys/types.h>
    #include <sys/socket.h>
    #include <netinet/in.h>
    #include <arpa/inet.h>
    #include "defs.h"
    
source file: 

    client.c
    server.c
    connect.c
    books.c
    lib.c

Makefile:
    Makefile

To compile and launch: 

    1. in first terminal type "make" and enter
    2. then in first terminal type "./server&" and enter
    3. in second terminal type "make" and enter
    4. then in second terminal type "./client" and enter
